---
title: Fragrant Chicken & Sweetcorn Soup with Udon Noodles & Asian Greens
description: Chicken and sweetcorn soup is an absolute classic, don’t you think? Tender chicken, slurp-worthy udon noodles and bursts of corn come together in a rich, savoury broth. A hit of ginger paste adds a punchy twist and you’ve got a cosy, flavour-packed bowl that’s pure comfort with every bite!
